{"data":{"page":{"html":"<h1 id=\"getting-started\"><a href=\"#getting-started\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Getting started</h1>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<h2><a href=\"#toc\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#about-hbase\">About HBase</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#installing-hbase\">Installing HBase</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#starting-hbase\">Starting HBase</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#installing-node-hbase\">Installing node-hbase</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#creating-a-new-instance\">Creating a new instance</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"about-hbase\"><a href=\"#about-hbase\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>About HBase</h2>\n<p>HBase is part of the Hadoop ecosystem from the Apache Software Foundation. It is a column oriented database (think NoSQL) that really scale and is modelled after Google papers and its BigTable database.</p>\n<h2 id=\"installing-hbase\"><a href=\"#installing-hbase\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installing HBase</h2>\n<p>Downloading the <a href=\"https://www.cloudera.com/downloads/quickstart_vms.html\">Cloudera CDH</a> or <a href=\"https://hortonworks.com/products/sandbox/\">Hortonworks HDP</a> sandboxes are the easiest ways to get started. If you run Ubuntu, Debian or RedHat, those two distributions provide packages integrated with apt-get and yum. It is also possible to download the binaries from the <a href=\"http://hbase.apache.org/\">official website</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"starting-hbase\"><a href=\"#starting-hbase\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Starting HBase</h2>\n<p>Assuming <code class=\"language-text\">${HBASE_HOME}/bin</code> is in your classpath, starting HBase with REST connector is as follow:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">start-hbase.sh\nhbase-daemon.sh start rest</code></pre></div>\n<p>And stopping:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hbase-daemon.sh stop rest\nstop-hbase.sh</code></pre></div>\n<p>Or</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">ps</span> ax <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> hbase <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">awk</span> <span class=\"token string\">'{print <span class=\"token variable\">$1</span>}'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">xargs</span> <span class=\"token function\">kill</span> -9</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"installing-node-hbase\"><a href=\"#installing-node-hbase\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installing node-hbase</h2>\n<p>Use NPM or YARN to install the HBase client.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> hbase</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"creating-a-new-instance\"><a href=\"#creating-a-new-instance\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Creating a new instance</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> hbase <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'hbase'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> client <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">hbase</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  host<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'127.0.0.1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  port<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">8080</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Or</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> hbase <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'hbase'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> client <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">hbase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Client</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  host<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'127.0.0.1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  port<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">8080</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Getting started","description":"Instructions on how to get up and running","keywords":"hbase, tutorial, quickstart, install, configuration, example"},"fields":{"edit_url":"https://github.com/adaltas/node-hbase-docs/edit/master/src/md/learn/quickstart.md"}}},"pageContext":{}}